 * Slideshow feature
 * Fix thumbnail left offset during thumb slide animations (so they go straight up rather than up and to one side) 
 * Video media support
 * Borders on thumbnails
 * Option to progressively pre-cache all images in the background rather than just precaching the images immediately to the left and right (better user experience, more bandwidth hungry)
 * Support disabled state
 * Support destroy method to put back original HTML
